Elves are an ancient race of highly intelligent demihumans who 
typically make their homes in forests, far away from most other 
races. They are very fair colored, and seem quite fragile. However, 
they are very lithe and quick. They have fine features and pointed 
ears, which many humans tend to find quite compelling. Elves are 
usually cautious adventurers, preferring to become great scholars 
instead. They have amassed some of the greatest libraries in the 
world. Elves value their independence and tend to hold themselves 
aloof from other people's affairs.

Elves are able to see in the dark.
 
Elves cannot take the Psionicist class.
